  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Demonstration of Mercury Reduction and Minimization in the Production of Vinyl Chloride Monomer in China</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. Strengthen institutional, regulatory, and enforcement (IRE) capacity in VCM production in China

,2. Promote technology transfer and investment for the widespread application of BAT/BEP

,3. Promote the recovery of mercury in mercury-containing waste from VCM production 

,4. Contaminated site identification and risk reduction associated with VCM production 

,5. Information dissemination and awareness raising among stakeholders

,6.Monitoring  Evaluation

,Project Management Cost</narrative>
  </description>
